Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)

[
    {
        "A": "entity 3 mod",
        "id": "E3",
        "type": "T"
    },
    {
        "A": "entity 4",
        "id": "E4",
        "type": "T"
    }
]


11. Get entities modified in the range from t_3 to t_4 -> E4
============================================================
